<h2 id="privacy_policy">Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>ShowMaker provides this Privacy Policy to inform you of our policies and procedures regarding the collection, use, disclosure and protection of information that apply to our service, as well as your choices regarding the collection and use of information.</p>

<h4 id="overview">Overview</h4>

<p>ShowMaker is an online service that provides tools for businesses to manage and sell event tickets over the internet. In order for our service to function we collect various information about your company as well as the customers that your company has business dealings with. As a general rule, ShowMaker will never share any of the information we collect with any third-party service.</p>

<h4 id="personally_identifiable_information">Personally Identifiable Information</h4>

<p>To use ShowMaker, a company name, an email address, user name and password are required. In order to use various portions of the service API credentials for third-party services are required. BrainTree, Stripe, and Square are examples of third-party services that we support and require authentication credentials be provided to us.</p>

<p>We protect all the information entrusted to us to the best of our abilities and do not allow anyone except senior engineering staff to view such information, and only for the purposes of debugging system and communication failures within our systems.</p>

