<p>Like many other websites, ShowMaker uses a standard technology called “cookies.” Cookies are small pieces of information that are stored on your hard drive and not on our site. Cookies help us understand how customers use our service, which allows us to improve and tailor the service. You will not be able to use the ShowMaker service if you disable cookies.</p>

